    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:1.1",
          "pli": "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. ",
          "en": "At Sāvatthī. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:1.2",
          "pli": "Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho so bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: ",
          "en": "Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:1.3",
          "pli": "“‘brahmacariyaṃ, brahmacariyan’ti, bhante, vuccati. ",
          "en": "“Sir, they speak of this thing called the ‘spiritual path’. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:1.4",
          "pli": "Katamaṃ nu kho, bhante, brahmacariyaṃ, katamaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti? ",
          "en": "What is the spiritual path? And what is the culmination of the spiritual path?” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:2.1",
          "pli": "“Ayameva kho, bhikkhu, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo brahmacariyaṃ, seyyathidaṃ—",
          "en": "“Mendicant, the spiritual path is simply this noble eightfold path, that is: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:2.2",
          "pli": "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi. ",
          "en": "right view, right thought, right speech, right action, right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:2.3",
          "pli": "Yo kho, bhikkhu, rāgakkhayo dosakkhayo mohakkhayo—",
          "en": "The ending of greed, hate, and delusion. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:2.4",
          "pli": "idaṃ brahmacariyapariyosānan”ti. ",
          "en": "This is the culmination of the spiritual path.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn45.6:2.5",
          "pli": "Chaṭṭhaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
